, {\"ngram\": \"other high-end competitions\", \"from\": 2222, \"to\": 2249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hence, the same format we see constantly.\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2292, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hence, the same format\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How much the IGF has lobbied them on other format is unclear.\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2306, \"end\": 2309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Golf_Federation\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.631154401675957e-13, \"text\": \"IGF\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Golf_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Golf_Federation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other format\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also, the IOC is obsessed by capping the field size due to lack of space in the Olympic Village for athletes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094even though virtually no golfers, especially the elite of the elite, will stay there.\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2366, \"end\": 2369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.250354120856171e-30, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2436, \"end\": 2451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.882251273131502e-21, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the field size\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2407}, {\"ngram\": \"lack\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2419}, {\"ngram\": \"space\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2428},