ents.\", \"from\": 3988, \"to\": 4062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4011, \"end\": 4021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"DeChambeau\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bryson_DeChambeau\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past two years\", \"from\": 3991, \"to\": 4009}, {\"ngram\": \"just 10 qualifying events\", \"from\": 4036, \"to\": 4061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Had he been earning any level of points via LIV Golf, he quite likely would be among the top four Americans and competing for a gold medal this week.\", \"from\": 4064, \"to\": 4213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4108, \"end\": 4116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LIV Golf\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LIV_Golf\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any level\", \"from\": 4084, \"to\": 4093}, {\"ngram\": \"points\", \"from\": 4097, \"to\": 4103}, {\"ngram\": \"the top four Americans\", \"from\": 4149, \"to\": 4171}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 4190, \"to\": 4202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Understandably, this has caused a good bit of angst and led to conjecture that the qualifying process be changed.\", \"from\": 4215, \"to\": 4328, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good bit\", \"from\": 4247, \"to\": 4257}, {\"ngram\": \"angst\", \"from\": 4261, \"to\": 4266}, {\"ngram\": \"the qualifying process\", \"from\": 4294, \"to\": 4316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI think it would be great if the countries can get to pick who they bring and just be like, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098hey, these are the guys that we believe have a chance to win a medal,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 or \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098this is the guys that I want to bring,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Ancer said.\", \"from\": 4330, \"to\": 4562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the countries\", \"from\": 4364, \"to\": 4377}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098hey\", \"from\": 4427, \"to\": 4433}, {\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 4445, \"to\": 4453}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 4475, \"to\": 4483}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 4491, \"to\": 4498}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099\", \"from\": 4499, \"to\": 4502}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098this\", \"from\": 4506, \"to\": 4513}, {\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 4517, \"to\": 4525}, {\"ngram\": \"Ancer\", \"from\": 4551, \"to\": 4556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMaybe that would be a way to fix it.\", \"from\": 4563, \"to\": 4602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 4586, \"to\": 4591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s not going to be easy.\", \"from\": 4603, \"to\": 4631, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 4603, \"to\": 4609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Not everybody is going to be happy.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d No doubt.\", \"from\": 4632, \"to\": 4681, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Not everybody\", \"from\": 4632, \"to\": 4645}, {\"ngram\": \"happy.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s true that other Olympic sports have qualification criteria that vary by country.\", \"from\": 4682, \"to\": 4773, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"But it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 4682, \"to\": 4692}, {\"ngram\": \"other Olympic sports\", \"from\": 4703, \"to\": 4723}, {\"ngram\": \"qualification criteria\", \"from\": 4729, \"to\": 4751}, {\"ngram\": \"country\", \"from\": 4765, \"to\": 4772}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI think you can always do it, like with other sports, and allow the countries to pick themselves,\\u00e2\\u